data.name: compositionRequireCommas.HelpString
data.value: If this is checked, the student is required to insert commas where shown in the sentences. If there are no commas in the sentences, this has no effect.

data.name: compositionCaseSensitive.HelpString
data.value: If this is checked, the student must use the exact casing shown. It is recommended that this be checked only if the exercise has capitalization problems.
